title: TDL Gun Dog Training Whistle with Lanyard - Dog Whistle with Loud, Solid Tone & Far Reaching Sound - Ideal High-Frequency Long-Distance Dog Recall Whistle for Most Breeds - Black with Black Rope
features: ✅ ENHANCED RECALL TRAINING: Our TDL Gundog Whistle is perfect for recall training, allowing you to establish a strong connection with your dog even at a far distance. Its louder sound projection ensures your commands are heard clearly, making recall training more effective and reliable.
✅ LOUDER SOUND: Our TDL Gun Dog Whistle boasts superior sound projection, ensuring your commands reach your dog even from greater distances, enhancing training effectiveness.
✅ SUPPORTING SMALL BUSINESSES Our business is a small family run business and we are grateful for every single order.

✅ NECK LANYARD: Easily wear the TDL Dog Whistle around your neck, allowing your hands to issue treats or engage in play easily. When not in use, hang it with leads, treat pouches, and other dog training aids.
✅ FOOD-GRADE PLASTIC: The TDL Dog Whistle model is non-toxic, durable, and easy to blow. Our Whistle measures just 8 cm x 1.9 cm for easy carrying with other dog essentials.

✅ CONSISTENT SOUND: The sound emitted by the TDL Dog Whistle is easily heard by dogs' ears. Its solid tone at a single high frequency enables the whole family to engage in consistent whistle-dog training. This frequency is suitable for most dog breeds, and specifically for Gun Dogs and Pointers that roam further.

✅ TRUSTED BY PROFESSIONALS: Trusted by trainers and dog owners alike, the TDL Gundog Whistle offers unparalleled performance, making it the preferred choice for effective and successful dog training sessions.
description: Product Description Suitable For All Breeds Our TDL Gundog Whistle is actually suitable for all breeds - the reason we call it the "gun dog" whistle is due to it's louder tone as it travels further. Gun dogs often often roam further, so it is helpful for the whistle tone to be able reach the dog.
